### ProductsService API Tests - MVC Architecture

### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7002
@token = 

### 1. Get all categories (public endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get all products (public endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Accept: application/json

### 3. Search products with filters (public endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/search?search=laptop&categoryId=1&minPrice=500&maxPrice=1000&page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### 4. Get category by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1
Accept: application/json

### 5. Get product by ID (requires authentication)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 6. Create new category (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Sports",
    "description": "Sports equipment and accessories"
}

### 7. Create new product (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Gaming Laptop ASUS ROG",
    "description": "High-performance gaming laptop with RTX 4080, 32GB RAM",
    "price": 2499.99,
    "categoryId": 1,
    "sku": "ASUS-ROG-G15-001",
    "stock": 10,
    "imageUrl": "https://example.com/gaming-laptop.jpg"
}

### 8. Update product (requires authentication)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated Laptop Dell Inspiron 15",
    "price": 849.99,
    "stock": 30
}

### 9. Update product stock (requires authentication)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1/stock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "quantity": 50
}

### 10. Update category (requires authentication)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Electronics & Gadgets",
    "description": "Updated description for electronics category"
}

### 11. Delete product (Admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Delete category (Admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/4
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Instructions:
# 1. Get a JWT token from UsersService login
# 2. Replace {{token}} with the actual token
# 3. Run the requests in order
